Overview

Unlock1. Clear the main story.
2. Finish the Gaibara side quest.
3. Finish the Naoki side quest.
4. Go to Bamboo Village.
5. Go to where the statue dedicated to Bufu was located.
EntranceBamboo Village (North side of village)
Floors99F (Can escape from 26F)
Bring ItemsNoAlliesNo
Bring GitanNoBring Level UpsYes
Starting ItemBufu's Cleaver, Big Riceball
